HEADWORD: drawknife
<hw>drawknife</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>see <er>drawing
knife</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> drawshave.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

